data.description: Builders, developers, investors check out this prime development opportunity.  7,015 sq ft lot in north Cherry Creek with original brick house and 2 car alley access garage. Wonderful opportunity to scrape and build your dream home or renovate.  Fantastic location. Walk to Cherry Creek Mall, restaurants, shops.    It's a corner lot near swanky 6th Ave with so much room to build on.  Buyer and/or Buyers agent must do their own due diligence as to what can be built on this lot but there are many new townhomes and duplexes built nearby. House is being sold strictly as is. Zoned G-RH-3.
